div.i: JamKazam is an online platform where musicians in separate locations can play together as if they were in the same room.

The site was created a few years ago. With the current crisis, musicians have been searching for an app like JamKazam.
However, getting the app to work takes specific hardware.The hardware is relatively inexpensive and can be purchased online.
